@startuml
title Factory Method - Ejemplo 2 - solucion para transporte logistico
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  ArrowColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
}
hide empty members

package "main" #EEF2FF {
  class Main <<cliente>>
}

package "pattern" #ECFDF5 {
  abstract class Logistics {
  }
  class RoadLogistics {
  }
  class SeaLogistics {
  }
  class Ship {
    +deliver(String packageId): void
  }
  interface Transport <<interfaz>> {
  }
  class Truck {
    +deliver(String packageId): void
  }
}

Logistics <|-- RoadLogistics
Logistics <|-- SeaLogistics
Transport <|.. Ship
Transport <|.. Truck
Logistics ..> Truck : crea
Logistics ..> Ship : crea
RoadLogistics ..> Truck : crea
RoadLogistics ..> Ship : crea
SeaLogistics ..> Ship : crea
Transport ..> Truck : crea
Transport ..> Ship : crea
Truck ..> Ship : crea
Main ..> Logistics : ejecuta

note bottom
La implementacion esta concentrada en src/pattern/PatternImplementation.java.
Main solo instancia y ejecuta el caso de uso.
end note
@enduml
